{
  "stem": "4226.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he also had cattle for, for feeding-- for slaughter, but he-- they were using from the mills.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, they had flour mill, oil, oil mill, and the spirits.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that was part of the other family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they, they were feeding these with grain, the, the animals.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, from the-- then that was in-- after Second World War, in, in 1928, they--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the First World War--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--they, they-- these lands were taken away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were given some coupons, which wasn't worth anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what was a lot people-- it was about-- we were left about 40 acres, something like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my father owned part of it because he kept selling it all the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then in the last three years, actually, he, he-- we had very little left, no more machinery.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had a, a shop-- he opened a shop in the same building, which sold groceries and hardware.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I really-- I really don't know what's--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, those 40 were not enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could produce enough for yourself, but not much to sell.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the grandfather had much more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was taken away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No food.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No food, except essentials of grocery, like salt, sugar--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--flours, that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it mainly were tools.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I can remember they did bartering.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some, some of the people came from distant villages, hours to buy sugar or salt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they didn't have money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They bartered eggs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fresh eggs or other products they produced, and they wanted sugar instead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you just had to calculate how many-- what was the price of the egg, and how much sugar they can buy for so many eggs.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That went on for years like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I remember it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
